WEBVTT

00:11.080 --> 00:12.040
This toughness isn't enough

00:12.320 --> 00:13.080
Have them revise it

00:15.080 --> 00:16.240
Not just swords and blades

00:16.400 --> 00:17.360
Horseshoes

00:17.440 --> 00:18.600
Tent stakes

00:18.840 --> 00:19.440
In the smallest details

00:19.440 --> 00:20.520
Everything must be done well

00:20.840 --> 00:21.560
Wutu's ironwork

00:21.560 --> 00:22.680
Is indeed inferior to ours now

00:23.000 --> 00:23.440
But this is not

00:23.440 --> 00:24.600
A reason to stand still

00:25.000 --> 00:25.880
Lack of men, lack of money

00:26.120 --> 00:26.920
Any difficulty

00:27.280 --> 00:28.200
Submit a memorial to me

00:28.600 --> 00:29.280
Yes, yes

00:29.600 --> 00:30.560
Prince of Jin

00:30.840 --> 00:32.200
Your subjects take leave

00:42.280 --> 00:42.800
Ruo Lan

00:46.200 --> 00:47.160
My brother wrote

00:47.400 --> 00:48.080
General Zu Kun

00:48.080 --> 00:49.200
Is preparing to return to the capital to report

00:49.400 --> 00:50.400
He's coming back with him

00:50.520 --> 00:51.720
General Zu Kun

00:54.720 --> 00:55.640
This time, Chen Dao

00:55.640 --> 00:57.760
Took the opportunity to transfer me to southeast Huiji County

00:58.200 --> 00:58.760
The purpose

00:58.760 --> 00:59.960
Is to completely

00:59.960 --> 01:01.960
Sever Your Highness's support

01:02.440 --> 01:03.040
Now

01:03.080 --> 01:04.000
General Zu Kun

01:04.000 --> 01:05.480
Is about to return to the capital to report

01:05.640 --> 01:07.480
Your Highness must take this seriously

01:07.720 --> 01:08.840
Supporting the northern expedition

01:08.840 --> 01:10.360
Is our last chance

01:10.480 --> 01:11.840
To win the people's hearts

01:12.000 --> 01:13.000
Your Highness must

01:13.000 --> 01:14.120
Seize this opportunity

01:14.280 --> 01:15.080
Find a way

01:15.080 --> 01:15.920
To gain

01:15.920 --> 01:17.480
General Zu Kun's approval

01:17.760 --> 01:18.280
This way

01:18.280 --> 01:20.280
We can turn the situation around

01:23.640 --> 01:24.920
General Zu Kun these years

01:25.720 --> 01:26.920
Hasn't taken any side

01:27.360 --> 01:29.080
Clearly doesn't want to wade into the capital's troubles

01:29.640 --> 01:31.200
But to push forward the northern expedition

01:31.280 --> 01:32.760
We still need to rely on the Zu family

01:36.360 --> 01:37.760
As for the northern expedition

01:37.760 --> 01:39.120
Only you are risking your life for it

01:49.840 --> 01:51.360
Sister's cooking is still the best

01:52.000 --> 01:53.000
Eating so fast

01:53.000 --> 01:54.280
General Zu doesn't feed us

01:55.720 --> 01:56.840
Military funds are tight

01:57.000 --> 01:58.360
The general wishes he could split one coin

01:58.480 --> 01:59.480
Into three pieces to spend

01:59.760 --> 02:00.480
I've been

02:00.560 --> 02:02.120
Starving nine meals in three days

02:02.760 --> 02:03.920
Crying poor won't help

02:04.120 --> 02:05.120
Eat less

02:05.480 --> 02:07.160
Your brother-in-law is also broke

02:08.480 --> 02:09.600
Brother-in-law
